启动）\n优化相册图片误删除问题，通过即时通知引导你前往相册&ldquo;最近删除&rdquo;查看\n\n【安全隐私】\n新增文件管理、便签和相册的最近删除入口支持密码校验，防止隐私泄露\n新增在手机管家的清理存储中，支持点击&ldquo;存储情况&rdquo;查看内存占用详情\n新增屏幕共享过程中支持屏蔽敏感应用和通知，保护隐私安全（设置-安全和隐私-屏幕共享保护）\n新增支持在更改密码 4 天内，若忘记密码，可通过旧密码重置\n\n【通信互联】\n新增小布通话支持智能识别外卖、快递、打车等高频来电场景，不仅能自动接听电话，还支持自定义回复话术；通话结束后，小布会生成智能摘要，并为你标识重点内容\n新增支持手机与 Windows 电脑 O+互联，实现跨端文件管理，让办公更方便\n优化手机查找功能，支持在主动关机或低电量自动关机时也能被发现，用机更放心\n\n【系统】\n新增通知堆叠效果，优化锁屏通知视觉和交互，视觉更美观，操作更简单\n新增锁屏界面向右滑动也可以进入乐划锁屏\n新增内容拖拽设置项，支持长按拖拽三方应用中的图片和文字（设置-辅助功能-内容拖拽）\n新增游戏内浮窗跳转功能，开启后在部分游戏内跳转至其它应用时，该应用将以浮窗打开（设置-辅助功能-自由浮窗-浮窗跳转）\n新增浮窗大小与位置记忆功能\n优化抽屉模式视觉和交互，视觉更一致，操作更便捷\n优化系统界面及图标，更美观\n优化浮窗、分屏应用窗口动效与兼容性，提升使用体验\n更新 Android 安全补丁至 2025 年 5 月，提升系统安全性","googlePatchDate":"2025/05/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.821CN01_2025052619020191.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23105_15.0.1_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP1/PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.821CN01_2025052619020191.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/06/10/87a829c3766b4de482a2604bb9db9cc2.zip","fileName":"PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.821CN01_2025052619020191.zip","md5":"b8b2c90398d73aa88a4f272fea139286","colorOs":"ColorOS 15.0.1","androidVersion":"Android 15","updateDescEnglish":"【AI】\nYou can now drag and drop text, images, or photos to Breeno and ask questions about them.\n\n【Apps】\nAdds the Translate app, which allows you to take photos of text to translate, as well as translate conversations and documents. It also includes live translation and supports additional languages.\nAdds a new widget with quick functions specifically tailored to elderly users to enhance usability.\nYou can now open games in muted mode when you want a distraction-free gaming experience. This feature can be found in &quot;Game Assistant - Tools - Play games muted&quot;.\nFixes an issue where photos might be accidentally deleted by a third-party app. When this happens, you will receive a notification to review deleted photos in Recently deleted.\n\n【Security &amp; privacy】\nYou can now protect your recently deleted items in the My Files, Notes, and Photos apps with a password for added privacy.\nYou can view storage usage by apps and the system when freeing up space using Phone Manager.\nDuring Screen sharing, you can block specific apps and notifications. This feature is available in &quot;Settings - Security &amp; privacy - Screen sharing protection&quot;.\nAfter changing your Lock screen password, you can reset it using the previous password.\n\n【Communication &amp; interconnection】\nBreeno Call can automatically identify food delivery, package delivery, ride-hailing, and other calls, and answer these calls on your behalf. You can customize the responses as needed. After a call ends, a summary highlighting key points will generated.\nThe O+ Connect app now supports Windows, allowing you to connect your mobile device to a Windows computer and manage files across devices effortlessly.\nYour devices are now findable even when they are powered off, either automatically or manually.\n\n【System】\nImproves the visuals for individual notifications, notification stacks, and user interactions with these notifications on the Lock screen.\nYou can now enter Lock Screen Magazine by swiping right on the Lock screen.\nAdds the Drag &amp; drop feature that allows you to use the gesture to perform actions on images and text in third-party apps. This feature can be turned on or off in &quot;Settings - Accessibility &amp; convenience - Drag &amp; drop&quot;.\nYou can now open a floating window when redirected to another app from a game. This feature can be turned on or off in &quot;Settings - Accessibility &amp; convenience - Floating Window - Redirect via floating window&quot;.\nThe size and position of floating windows are now saved for more convenient usage.\nRedesigns the app drawer for a more consistent visual style, improving usability throughout the interface.\nImproves the user interface and icon designs.\nImproves the animations and compatibility for floating windows and Split View.\nIntegrates the May 2025 Android security patch to enhance system security.","companyName":null,"fileSize":10232326488,"softwareVersion":"15.0.0.821(CN01)","projectNo":"23105","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[]},{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/05/26/d19a3583065b49d98d437782949e93b3.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/05/26/d19a3583065b49d98d437782949e93b3.zip","marketModel":"OPPO Find X8 Pro","updateDesc":null,"googlePatchDate":"2025/05/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.820CN01_2025042701210138.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23105_15.0.1_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP1/PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.820CN01_2025042701210138.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/05/26/d19a3583065b49d98d437782949e93b3.zip","fileName":"PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.820CN01_2025042701210138.zip","md5":"e604618ef6c2fc6bf79ae4f9c9d601af","colorOs":"ColorOS 15.0.1","androidVersion":"Android 15","updateDescEnglish":null,"companyName":null,"fileSize":10232314912,"softwareVersion":"15.0.0.820(CN01)","projectNo":"23105","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[]}]}]},{"osVersion":"ColorOS 15.0.2","packageInfo":[{"versionType":"normal","packageInfoDetail":[{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/09/19/fcee8ea8aa9545328f70516379eaabef.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/09/19/fcee8ea8aa9545328f70516379eaabef.zip","marketModel":"OPPO Find X8 Pro","updateDesc":null,"googlePatchDate":"2025/09/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.860CN01_2025082523540219.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23105_15.0.2_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP5/PKC110domestic_11_15.0.0.860CN01_2025082523540219.zip","filePath